README: Product Review Summarizer and Sentiment Analyzer
📦 Project Description
This is a full-stack web application designed to help users summarize, analyze, and compare Amazon product reviews using AI. It uses OpenAI GPT-3.5 for natural language summarization, custom ML models for sentiment and star rating prediction, and Selenium for live review scraping. The tool features a web interface built with Flask and JavaScript, supporting both static and live analysis of product reviews.
🚀 Features

• Summarize reviews using GPT-3.5  
• Predict sentiment breakdown (positive, neutral, negative)  
• Predict star ratings from text  
• Compare two products side by side  
• Scrape live Amazon product reviews via URL  
• Chatbot answers custom product-related questions  
• Visualize sentiment in charts and show predicted star icons

🛠️ Setup Instructions

1. Clone or download the repository.
2. Install the required packages:  
   pip install -r requirements.txt
3. Download ChromeDriver and ensure it matches your Chrome version.
4. Add your OpenAI API key as an environment variable or in a `.env` file:
   OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
5. Run the Flask app:
   cd Project  
   python app.py
6. Open http://127.0.0.1:5000 in your browser.

